nable custom Visibility Statuses'=>'Mú awọn ipo Fifi hàn ti a ṣe adani ṣiṣẹ','Posts with custom Visibility also require status-specific capabilities for editing'=>'Awọn ifiweranṣẹ pẹlu Fifi hàn ti a ṣe adani tun nilo awọn agbara pato ipo fun ṣiṣatunkọ','lock'=>'di','If the Published visibility status is locked, also prevent posts from being unpublished.'=>'Ti ipo fifi hàn ti a tẹjade ba ti di, tun ṣe idiwọ awọn ifiweranṣẹ lati di atẹjade.','If enabled, users need the %s to unpublish a post.'=>'Ti a ba mu ṣiṣẹ, awọn olumulo nilo %s lati yọ ifiweranṣẹ kuro ni atẹjade.','If enabled, users will need an additional role capability to unpublish a post.'=>'Ti a ba mu ṣiṣẹ, awọn olumulo yoo nilo agbara ipa afikun lati yọ ifiweranṣẹ kuro ni atẹjade.','Select...'=>'Yan...','Re-run Planner import (with Status Control properties, ordering)'=>'Tun ṣiṣe gbigbe wọle Planner (pẹlu awọn ohun-ini Iṣakoso Ipo, iṣọkan)','Re-run Planner import (ignoring Status Control configuration)'=>'Tun ṣiṣe gbigbe wọle Planner (foju kọ iṣeto Iṣakoso Ipo)','Re-run Planner import'=>'Tun ṣiṣe gbigbe wọle Planner','Status color, icon and position is automatically imported from PublishPress Planner. Select an option above to re-run the import, giving priority to Planner-defined status position.'=>'Awọ ipo, aami ati ipo ni a gbe wọle laifọwọyi lati PublishPress Planner. Yan aṣayan loke lati tun ṣe gbigbe wọle, fifun ni pataki si ipo ipo ti Planner ti ṣalaye.','Back up current colors, icons, labels and post types'=>'Ṣe afẹyinti awọn awọ, awọn aami, awọn aami ati awọn iru ifiweranṣẹ lọwọlọwọ','Restore backup of status colors'=>'Mú afẹyinti awọn awọ ipo pada','Restore backup of status icons'=>'Mú afẹyinti awọn aami ipo pada','Restore backup of status labels'=>'Mú afẹyinti awọn aami ipo pada','Restore backup of status post types'=>'Mú afẹyinti awọn iru ifiweranṣẹ ipo pada','Restore auto-backup of status colors'=>'Tun pada afẹyinti aifọwọyi ti awọn awọ ipo','Restore auto-backup of status icons'=>'Tun pada afẹyinti aifọwọyi ti awọn aami ipo','Restore auto-backup of status labels'=>'Tun pada afẹyinti aifọwọyi ti awọn lẹta ipo','Restore auto-backup of status post types'=>'Tun pada afẹyinti aifọwọyi ti awọn iru ifiweranṣẹ ipo','Use default status colors'=>'Lo awọn awọ ipo aiyipada','Use default status icons'=>'Lo awọn aami ipo aiyipada','Use default status labels'=>'Lo awọn lẹta ipo aiyipada','Use default status post types'=>'Lo awọn iru ifiweranṣẹ ipo aiyipada','Use Planner plugin\'s default status colors'=>'Lo awọn awọ ipo aiyipada ti ohun itanna Planner','Use Planner plugin\'s default status icons'=>'Lo awọn aami ipo aiyipada ti ohun itanna Planner','Edit Status: %s'=>'Ṣatunkọ Ipo: %s','Edit %1$s: %2$s'=>'Ṣatunkọ %1$s: %2$s','Edit Status Labels: %s'=>'Ṣatunkọ Awọn aami Ipo: %s','Edit %1$s Labels: %2$s'=>'Ṣatunkọ Awọn aami %1$s: %2$s','Add New Pre-Publication Status'=>'Fi Ipo Tuntun Pre-Publication kun','For custom Visibility Statuses, %1$supgrade to PublishPress Statuses Pro%2$s.'=>'Fun awọn ipo Wiwo aṣa, %1$s ṣe imudojuiwọn si PublishPress Statuses Pro %2$s.','Note: Custom Visibility Statuses are %1$sdisabled%2$s.'=>'Akiyesi: Awọn ipo Wiwo aṣa ni %1$s ti wa ni pipade %2$s.','Pre-Publication'=>'Pre-Publication','Visibility'=>'Wiwo','Revision'=>'Atunṣe','This status can be assigned to an unpublished post using the Post Status dropdown.'=>'Ipo yii le ṣee fi assign si ifiweranṣẹ ti a ko tẹjade nipa lilo akojọ aṣayan Ipo Ifiweranṣẹ.','Integration'=>'Isopọ','Editor'=>'Oníṣàkóso','Advanced'=>'Ìtẹ̀siwaju','License'=>'Ìwé-ẹ̀rí','Sorry, you do not have permission to edit custom statuses.'=>'Ẹ jọ̀ọ́, o kò ní ẹ̀tọ́ láti ṣàtúnṣe ipo àṣà.','Please enter a name for the status'=>'Ẹ jọ̀ọ́, tẹ orúkọ kan fún ipo àṣà','Please enter a slug for the status'=>'Ẹ jọ̀ọ́, tẹ slug kan fún ipo àṣà','Please enter a valid, non-numeric name for the status.'=>'Ẹ jọ̀ọ́, tẹ orúkọ tó jẹ́wọ́, tí kò ní nọ́mbà fún ipo àṣà.','Status name cannot exceed 20 characters. Please try a shorter name.'=>'Orúkọ ipo àṣà kò le kọja awọn ohun kikọ 20. Ẹ jọ̀ọ́, gbìmọ́ orúkọ kékèké kan.','Status slug cannot exceed 20 characters. Please try a shorter name.'=>'Slug ipo àṣà kò le kọja awọn ohun kikọ 20. Ẹ jọ̀ọ́, gbìmọ́ orúkọ kékèké kan.','Name conflicts with existing status. Please choose another.'=>'Orúkọ náà nìkan ni ipò àṣà tó wà. Ẹ jọ̀ọ́, yan míràn.','Status name is restricted. Please choose another name.'=>'Orúkọ ipo àṣà ni ìdíwọ́. Ẹ jọ̀ọ́, yan orúkọ míràn.','Could not add status: '=>'A kò le fi ipo àṣà kun: ','Status does not exist.'=>'Ipo àṣà kò wà.','Could not delete the status: '=>'A kò le pa ipo àṣà: ','Post status doesn\'t exist.'=>'Ipo àṣà ìròyìn kò wà.','Error updating post status.'=>'Aṣiṣe kan ṣẹlẹ̀ ní imudojuiwọn ipo àṣà ìròyìn.','Error updating post status labels.'=>'Aṣiṣe ni imudojuiwọn awọn aami ipo ifiweranṣẹ.','Cannot reassign to the status you want to delete'=>'A kò le tún fi ipo àṣà náà sílẹ̀ tí o fẹ́ pa','Restricted status '=>'Ipo àṣà tí a fi ofin pa ','Status deleted'=>'Ipo àṣà ti pa','Status positions were not sent.'=>'Àwọn ipo àṣà kò ránṣẹ́.','Position'=>'Ipo','Status Name'=>'Orukọ Ipo','Upgrade to create an approval workflow for published content'=>'Gba imudojuiwọn lati ṣẹda ilana ifọwọsi fun akoonu ti a tẹjade','Create approval workflows using PublishPress Statuses Pro together with the PublishPress Revisions Pro plugin'=>'Ṣẹda awọn ilana ifọwọsi nipa lilo PublishPress Statuses Pro pọ pẹlu pẹpẹ PublishPress Revisions Pro','The PublishPress Revisions plugin allows users to submit changes to published posts'=>'Pẹpẹ PublishPress Revisions n gba awọn olumulo laaye lati fi awọn ayipada silẹ si awọn ifiweranṣẹ ti a tẹjade','PublishPress Statuses plugin enables you to add statuses for post changes created with Revisions'=>'Pẹpẹ PublishPress Statuses n jẹ ki o fi awọn ipo kun fun awọn ayipada ifiweranṣẹ ti a ṣẹda pẹlu Revisions','Each post type can have different Revisions statuses'=>'Iru ifiweranṣẹ kọọkan le ni awọn ipo Revisions ti o yatọ','You choose which users can manage content in each Revisions status'=>'O yan awọn olumulo wo ni o le ṣakoso akoonu ni ipo Revisions kọọkan','Premium Feature'=>'Iṣẹ Amuṣiṣẹpọ','Install Statuses Pro to unlock custom revision statuses.'=>'Fi Statuses Pro sori ẹrọ lati ṣii awọn ipo atunṣe aṣa.','Configure for any post type and role to match your editing workflow.'=>'Ṣeto fun iru ifiweranṣẹ eyikeyi ati ipa lati ba ilana ṣiṣatunkọ rẹ mu.','To define and control Revision statuses, update the %1$sPublishPress Revisions%2$s plugin to version %3$s or higher.'=>'Lati ṣalaye ati ṣakoso awọn ipo Revision, mu %1$sPublishPress Revisions%2$s pẹpẹ si ẹya %3$s tabi ga julọ.','Main Workflow:'=>'Ilana Pataki:','Drop any status here to include it in main workflow for new posts.'=>'Sọ ipo eyikeyi nibi lati fi kun si ilana pataki fun awọn ifiweranṣẹ titun.','Statuses in the main workflow are presented for convenient default selection when updating an unpublished post.'=>'Awọn ipo ninu ilana pataki ni a ṣe afihan fun yiyan aiyipada ti o rọrun nigbati n ṣe imudojuiwọn ifiweranṣẹ ti a ko tẹjade.','Statuses outside the main workflow are manually selectable when editing an unpublished post.'=>'Awọn ipo ti o wa ni ita ilana pataki ni a le yan ni ọwọ nigbati n ṣatunkọ ifiweranṣẹ ti a ko tẹjade.','Drop any status here to make it manually selectable outside the main workflow.'=>'Sọ ipo eyikeyi nibi lati jẹ ki o le yan ni ọwọ ni ita ilana pataki.','Drop any status here to disable.'=>'Sọ ipo eyikeyi nibi lati mu un ṣiṣẹ.','Standard Publication:'=>'Iwe Itẹsiwaju Boṣewa:','Visibility Statuses for Private Publication:'=>'Ipo Wo fun Iwe Itẹsiwaju Aladani:','Alternate Workflows:'=>'Awọn ọna iṣẹ miiran:','Disabled Statuses (drag to re-enable):'=>'Ipo ti a ti pa (fa lati tun mu ṣiṣẹ):','Upgrade to choose who can view your non-public posts'=>'Gba igbesoke lati yan ẹni ti o le wo awọn ifiweranṣẹ rẹ ti kii ṣe ti gbogbo eniyan','Upgrade to PublishPress Statuses Pro to define your own custom visibility statuses.'=>'Gba igbesoke si PublishPress Statuses Pro lati ṣe idanimọ awọn ipo ifihan aṣa tirẹ.','Create multiple visibility statuses to show content to different users'=>'Ṣẹda ọpọlọpọ awọn ipo ifihan lati fi akoonu han si awọn olumulo oriṣiriṣi','Choose which user roles can see posts in each status'=>'Yan awọn ipa olumulo wo ni o le rii awọn ifiweranṣẹ ni ipo kọọkan','Select which user roles can move posts to each status'=>'Yan awọn ipa olumulo wo ni o le gbe awọn ifiweranṣẹ si ipo kọọkan','Decide which user roles can edit posts in each status'=>'Pinnu awọn ipa olumulo wo ni o le satunkọ awọn ifiweranṣẹ ni ipo kọọkan','%s, more...'=>'%s, diẹ sii...','No custom statuses found.'=>'Ko si ipo aṣa ti a ri.','Core'=>'Ipele','Default'=>'Aiyipada','Delete'=>'Pa','post action/button labelPitch'=>'Titaja']];